********************************************************************************
*                   Serial Lossless DPCM with Huffman coding                   *
********************************************************************************
* Differential Pulse Code Modulation (DPCM) with Huffman coding provies a      *
* higher compression with less computation than that of other Lossless JPEG    *
* methods. Huffman coding has not been added yet, instead Entropy calculations *
* have been added to get an approximate value for the compression ratio.       *
********************************************************************************